PyTetris is a very simple Tetris clone write by python+pygame.
To run it, you need to have python and pygame installed in your system.

Run it is very simple. Under Windows, just double click "pytetris.py".
And under linux, at first change your current work directory to where the
source code is, then issue either command in the terminal should be enough:
$ ./pytetris.py
$ python pytetris.py
